<div class="tb"><h1>Automated Notification of Local Events</h1>
        <ul class="navigation byline">
            <li><a class="nolink">Posted by </a><a href="../../profile/JordanFishman">Jordan Fishman</a><a class="nolink"> on February 9, 2012 at 7:17pm</a></li>
            <li><a class="xg_sprite xg_sprite-view" href="../../forum/topic/listForContributor?user=0449xxahohkta">View Discussions</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
    <div class="xg_module_body">
        <div class="discussion" data-category-id="">
            <div class="description">
                                <div class="xg_user_generated">
                    <p>Looks like I'm the first post on the new site's forum, wow this feels weird . . .</p>
<p>A friend recently introduced me to the community and I would love to join the next local event.  Are there (or will there be) any mechanisms on the site for email notification of upcoming events in certain regions?</p>
<p>If it was right in front of me I'll be sure to give myself a head slap.</p>
<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>- J</p>                </div>
            </div>
