                        <div class="description" id="desc_6456126Comment9043"><div class="xg_user_generated"><p>Hi Abdu,</p>
<p>As I understand it, the issue was that events are registered in a distributed/adhoc manner.</p>
<p>As a result we don't always have the necessary information.  There isn't a single form on a web page that people register their events through.  Also, this has gone international so we'd need something beyond zip.</p>
<p>Good call on the code though.</p></div></div>
